sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Cliente WiFi
  participant R as OpenWrt
  participant S as Pi 3B Sensor
  participant M as Mosquitto
  participant A as ai-analyzer
  participant L as llama.cpp
  participant D as Dashboard

  C->>R: Genera trafico real
  S->>S: Captura paquetes con tshark
  S->>S: Agrega estadisticas por 30s
  S->>R: Consulta leases, conntrack y allowed_clients
  S->>M: Publica batch JSON
  M->>A: Entrega evento MQTT
  A->>A: Persiste batch en SQLite
  A->>L: POST /completion con prompt de seguridad
  L-->>A: Analisis + riesgo
  A->>D: Publica historial, stats y stream SSE
